<head>UNIVERSAL</head>
    <list type="translations">
        <item xml:lang="zh">全宇宙的</item>
    </list>
<div type="definition">
<p>TRUE EVERYWHERE IN the WORLD AND IN the UNIVERSE.</p>
    <div type="definition" resp="#CH" modified="2023-09-13T01:51:15.142+09:00">
            <p>TRUE EVERYWHERE IN the WORLD.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
<div type="notes">
<div type="old-chinese-contrasts">
<p>Galilei was apparently the first to claim that his laws of nature applied everywhere in the universe, that there was not one law for the Heavens and another for the nether world, as Aristotle thought.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
